Class EventDetailsPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pom.crimson.base.BaseFixture
      • com.pom.crimson.base.BasePage
        • com.pom.crimson.pages.EventDetailsPage

  • public class EventDetailsPage
extends BasePage
    This is the Page Class for Event details page in the mobile application.
    User can navigate to this page by going to:

    Clicking on any event card from home page or Live Events page or All events page

    This page class contains MobileElements on this page and functions to simulate interactions with these elements.
    Author:
    Sivaprakash.Selvaraj
